data.description: This custom Craftsman lake front home in Carolina Trace's Golf East community, offers an ideal location near Raleigh, Pinehurst, & Fayetteville. The house features a well-designed layout with high ceilings & white oak floors on the main floor. The main floor includes owner's & guest suites, a dining room, a spacious kitchen, two living rooms w/ fireplaces, & a screened porch with Eze-Breeze Windows. Stunning views are visible from every room. The lower level has 9-foot ceilings, two more bedroom suites, a family room opening to a covered porch with a hot tub, & a gently sloped backyard leading to a custom dock. Additional amenities include an on-demand Generac Generator, lake-sourced irrigation, Invisible Fence, a grilling deck, & a three-bay garage for two cars and a golf cart.
